<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <title>
      Verifie ton email - Trackr
    </title>
  </head>
  <body
    style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f8f8f8; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;"
  >
    <table
      role="presentation"
      width="100%"
      cellspacing="0"
      cellpadding="0"
      border="0"
      style="background-color: #f8f8f8;"
    >
      <tr>
        <td align="center" style="padding: 48px 24px;">
          <table
            role="presentation"
            width="520"
            cellspacing="0"
            cellpadding="0"
            border="0"
            style="max-width: 520px; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden;"
          >

            <!-- Header -->
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 32px 40px 24px 40px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;">
                <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
                  <tr>
                    <td valign="middle" style="padding-right: 10px;">
                      <img
                        src="https://cdn.trackrr.app/images/branding/trackr-logo.png"
                        alt="Trackr"
                        width="28"
                        height="32"
                        style="display: block;"
                      />
                    </td>
                    <td valign="middle">
                      <span style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: #955ae9; letter-spacing: -0.5px;">Trackr</span>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- Content -->
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 40px;">
                <h1
                  style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; color: #1a1a1a; letter-spacing: -0.3px;"
                >
                  Verifie ton email
                </h1>

                <p style="margin: 0 0 24px 0; font-size: 15px; color: #555555; line-height: 1.6;">
                  Salut {{ displayName }}, confirme ton adresse email pour finaliser ton compte Trackr.
                </p>

                <div style="text-align: center; margin: 32px 0;">
                  <a
                    href="{{ verifyUrl }}"
                    style="display: inline-block; background-color: #955ae9; color: #ffffff; padding: 14px 32px; border-radius: 10px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; font-size: 15px;"
                  >
                    Verifier mon email
                  </a>
                </div>

                <div
                  style="margin: 24px 0; padding: 16px; background-color: #fafafa; border-radius: 10px; border-left: 3px solid #e5e5e5;"
                >
                  <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 13px; color: #666666; line-height: 1.5;">
                    Ce lien expire dans <strong>24 heures</strong>. Si vous n'avez pas cree de compte, ignorez cet email.
                  </p>
                </div>

                <p style="margin: 24px 0 0 0; font-size: 13px; color: #888888; line-height: 1.5;">
                  Si le bouton ne fonctionne pas, copiez ce lien dans votre navigateur :
                </p>
                <p
                  style="margin: 8px 0 0 0; font-size: 12px; color: #955ae9; word-break: break-all; line-height: 1.5;"
                >
                  {{ verifyUrl }}
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- Footer -->
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 24px 40px 32px 40px; border-top: 1px solid #f0f0f0;">
                <p style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; font-size: 13px; color: #888888; line-height: 1.5;">
                  Cet email a ete envoye par Trackr. Si vous avez des questions, contactez-nous a <a href="mailto:support@trackrr.app" style="color: #955ae9; text-decoration: none;">support
                    @trackrr.app
                  </a>
                </p>
                <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; color: #aaaaaa;">
                  © 2026 Trackr · <a href="https://trackrr.app/privacy" style="color: #aaaaaa; text-decoration: none;">Politique de confidentialite</a>· <a href="https://trackrr.app/terms" style="color: #aaaaaa; text-decoration: none;">Conditions</a>
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>

          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
